document_name: Minutes of the Project Board Meeting_November 2011

outputs.output_descr: The project will assist in developing capacity to formulate, mobilize finance and implement low-emission development strategies, support in fulfilling commitments under the UNFCCC to enable the country to make informed policy and investment decisions that reduce GHG emissions, reduce poverty, are inclusive, create new employment opportunities and green jobs and move societies towards long term sustainability.

project_descr: National capacity for effective transition to a low-emission development path enhanced
project_title: Supporting Uzbekistan in transition to a LED path
